OL,3,CDrone pilot came within seconds of
OL,4,Ccausing 'catastrophic' helicopter crash
OL,6,FAn amateur drone pilot who almost
OL,7,Fcaused a "catastrophic" crash with a
OL,8,Fpolice helicopter has been spared a
OL,9,Fprison sentence.
OL,11,FNathan Flint, 19, flew his DJI Air 3
OL,12,Fdrone four times higher than the 400ft
OL,13,Flegal limit in Middleton, and came
OL,14,Fwithin five seconds of crashing into a
OL,15,Fpolice helicopter with three people on
OL,16,Fboard.
OL,18,FIt was only because the helicopter's
OL,19,Fex-military pilot's spotted the drone
OL,20,Fand banked to the right that a crash
OL,21,Fwas avoided.
