OL,6,FThe pilot spotted the lights flying
OL,7,Fbelow the helicopter "in the 11
OL,8,Fo'clock position" and immediately
OL,9,F"took evasive action", prosecutor
OL,10,FAubrey Sampson told Manchester's
OL,11,FMinshull Street Court.
OL,13,FHe went on to say: "(The pilot) is of
OL,14,Fthe view taking immediate evasive
OL,15,Faction was necessary as the drone
OL,16,Fcould have made contact with the
OL,17,Faircraft within 4.8 seconds."
