OL,6,FThe captain of the police helicopter,
OL,7,FPeter Delaney, told police: "In all my
OL,8,Fyears as a helicopter pilot and before
OL,9,Fduring my military service I have
OL,10,Fnever had to take such evasive action
OL,11,Fbecause of a drone. It posed a huge
OL,12,Frisk to my aircraft... It could have
OL,13,Fcaused catastrophic results."
OL,15,FOne of the helicopters police
OL,16,Fpassengers saw the drone between 100
OL,17,Fand 200ft below the chopper and about
OL,18,F1,600ft from the ground, the court
OL,19,Fheard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
