OL,6,FThe drone then descended into the back
OL,7,Fgarden of Flint's home in Middleton
OL,8,Fand the second police passenger used
OL,9,F"mapping technology" to pinpoint
OL,10,FFlint's address on Talkin Drive. When
OL,11,Fthe helicopter returned to Manchester
OL,12,FCity Airport, a report of the 'near
OL,13,Fmiss' was filed..
OL,15,FThe next day police visited Flint's
OL,16,Fhome and arrested him. In his police
OL,17,Finterview, he admitted "straight away"
OL,18,Fhe was the pilot of the drone, adding
OL,19,Fthat he was "very excited" as he had
OL,20,Fpurchased the drone with his birthday
OL,21,Fmoney, at the cost of #1,200.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
