OL,6,FThe judge added: "You took ownership
OL,7,Fof the drone following a birthday and
OL,8,Ftook the opportunity to fly that drone
OL,9,Fand fly it in a way that was
OL,10,Fdangerous."
OL,12,FJudge Lester-Ashworth said she 'noted'
OL,13,Fthat the defendant had since sold the
OL,14,Fdrone, adding: "I doubt you have any
OL,15,Fintention of buying another one.
