OL,3,CDrone pilot came within seconds of
OL,4,Ccausing 'catastrophic' helicopter crash
OL,6,FShe added: "I'm not going to send you
OL,7,Fto prison today because of those
OL,8,Fneeds."
OL,10,FThe judge noted the defendant was
OL,11,Fstill 19, had no previous convictions,
OL,12,Fhad admitted his crimes and had
OL,13,F"demonstrated remorse".
OL,15,FShe said: "You did not intend to put
OL,16,Fothers at risk and you were ignorant
OL,17,Fto the risk you were posing."
OL,19,FThe judge added: "It's clearly a very
OL,20,Fdangerous offence and the consequences
OL,21,Fcould have been catastrophic."
