OL,6,FFlint, who is on benefits, was handed
OL,7,Fa community order and a three-month
OL,8,Felectronically-monitored curfew which
OL,9,Frequires him to be at home between 7pm
OL,10,Fand 8am.
OL,12,FHe was also ordered to pay #150
OL,13,Ftowards prosecution costs after he
OL,14,Fadmitted recklessly endangering an
OL,15,Faircraft, failing to comply with the
OL,16,Fmaximum operating height, failing to
OL,17,Fdisplay a registration, contravening
OL,18,Fregistration requirements and failing
OL,19,Fto have appropriate competence for the
OL,20,Fflight.
